OL,3,CGuernsey income tax to rise by 2% for
OL,4,Cnext two years
OL,6,FGuernsey earners will pay an
OL,7,Fadditional 2% on their income tax if
OL,8,Fthe States of Guernsey's budget
OL,9,Fproposals are approved.
OL,11,FThe increase will be a temporary
OL,12,Fmeasure for two years under proposals
OL,13,Fpublished today (Tuesday 8 October) by
OL,14,Fthe Policy & Resources (P&R) Committee.
OL,16,FIt comes as the States originally
OL,17,Fforecast that they would be operating
OL,18,Fat a surplus of #11.4 million in 2024.
OL,20,FHowever, this has turned into an
OL,21,Fexpected deficit of #24.4 million.
