OL,3,CGuernsey income tax to rise by 2% for
OL,4,Cnext two years
OL,6,FP&R believes the income tax rise will
OL,7,Fraise additional revenues of #34
OL,8,Fmillion each year.
OL,10,FThe Committee has also proposed
OL,11,Fseveral measures they claim will
OL,12,Fprotect lower and middle earners,
OL,13,Fincluding increasing the personal
OL,14,Fincome tax allowance, and freezing
OL,15,Falcohol duty.
OL,17,FThe personal income tax will rise to
OL,18,F#15,000 - a rise of #1,100 from the
OL,19,Fcurrent level.
