OL,3,CGuernsey income tax to rise by 2% for
OL,4,Cnext two years
OL,6,FP&R President, Deputy Lyndon Trott,
OL,7,Fclaims that this budget is not just
OL,8,F"balancing the books", but focussing
OL,9,Fon investing in what he describes as
OL,10,FGuernsey's "ageing infrastructure" and
OL,11,Fstabilising the States' financial
OL,12,Fposition.
OL,14,FHe explains: "While it would have been
OL,15,Feasier for our Committee to propose a
OL,16,Fminimalist, steady as she goes Budget
OL,17,Fthat made few waves as we head towards
OL,18,Fan election, it would have also been
OL,19,Fthe irresponsible thing to do.
