OL,6,F"We cannot in good conscience
OL,7,Fknowingly leave public finances in
OL,8,Fsuch a challenging state for our
OL,9,Fsuccessors to pick up.
OL,11,F"We must collectively take action and
OL,12,Fwe believe our package of measures
OL,13,Fwill be easily understood by the
OL,14,Fcommunity, are forthright in their
OL,15,Fintentions, and will raise the money
OL,16,Fwe need in the short term while
OL,17,Fprotecting the lowest income
OL,18,Fhouseholds."
OL,20,FMore updates from Guernsey's 2025
OL,21,FBudget to follow...
